<p><b>Umesh Virkumar <a href="/wiki/Vazirani" title="Vazirani">Vazirani</a></b> (<a href="/wiki/Hindi_language" title="Hindi language" class="mw-redirect">Hindi</a>: <span lang="hi">उमेश वीरकुमार वज़ीरानी</span>) is the Roger A. Strauch Professor of Electrical Engineering and Computer Science at the <a href="/wiki/University_of_California,_Berkeley" title="University of California, Berkeley">University of California, Berkeley</a>, and the director of the Berkeley Quantum Computation Center. His research interests lie primarily in <a href="/wiki/Quantum_computing" title="Quantum computing">quantum computing</a>. He is also the author of a textbook on algorithms.</p>
<p></p>
